OL,7,FPersonal Independent Payment (PIP) was
OL,8,Fone of the areas the prime minister
OL,9,Ffocused on in his speech, and the
OL,10,Freforms he announced will likely cause
OL,11,Falarm to those claiming it, as
OL,12,FPolitical Correspondent Carl Dinnen
OL,13,Fexplains
OL,15,FRishi Sunak has set out his "moral
OL,16,Fmission" to reform the welfare system
OL,17,Fas he called for more people to get
OL,18,Fback to work.
