OL,7,FThe prime minister warned against
OL,8,F"over-medicalising everyday challenges
OL,9,Fand worries of life" in a speech on
OL,10,FFriday, as he raised concerns about
OL,11,Fgrowing numbers of people deemed
OL,12,Fmedically unfit for work, which have
OL,13,Frisen sharply since the pandemic.
OL,15,FHe repeatedly stressed the system as
OL,16,Fit stands is letting people down by
OL,17,Fnot being focused enough on the work
OL,18,Fthey might be able to do, rather than
OL,19,Fwhat they can't do.
