OL,7,FOf those who are economically
OL,8,Finactive, half report suffering from
OL,9,Fdepression or anxiety, said the PM -
OL,10,Fbut data shows most of those report
OL,11,Fthese illnesses as secondary
OL,12,Fconditions rather than the main one
OL,13,Fkeeping them out of work.
OL,15,FThe PM's proposals have been met with
OL,16,Ffierce criticism, with disability
OL,17,Fcharity Scope describing it as a "full-
OL,18,Fon assault on disabled people".
