OL,8,Fthe government "has broken the NHS"
OL,9,Fand urged it to instead focus on
OL,10,Freducing the waiting list to get
OL,11,Fpeople back to work.
OL,13,FThe British Medical Association echoed
OL,14,FSir Keir's calls and criticised Mr
OL,15,FSunak's "hostile rhetoric on sicknote
OL,16,Fculture" and cited the need to tackle
OL,17,Flengthy waiting lists in the NHS to
OL,18,Fget people the care they need.
