OL,8,Fwelfare reforms were lacking in
OL,9,Fcompassion, saying "the exact opposite
OL,10,Fis true".
OL,12,F"Of course, those with serious
OL,13,Fdebilitating conditions should never
OL,14,Fbe expected to work," he said.
OL,16,F"But if you have a low-level mobility
OL,17,Fissue, your employer could make
OL,18,Freasonable adjustments."
