OL,7,FHe suggested greater medical evidence
OL,8,Fcould be required to substantiate a
OL,9,Fclaim for personal independence
OL,10,Fpayments (PIP), and that some people
OL,11,Fwith mental health conditions may be
OL,12,Foffered talking therapies or respite
OL,13,Fcare rather than cash transfers.
OL,15,FThe PM said: "We now spend #69 billion
OL,16,Fon benefits for people of working age
OL,17,Fwith a disability or health condition.
OL,19,F"That's more than our entire schools
OL,20,Fbudget, more than our transport
OL,21,Fbudget, more than our policing budget.
